Type: Package
Version: 0.99.1
Package: SpatialData
Title: S4 classes to represent scverse's 'SpatialData' in R
Description:
  Defines S4 classes to represent scverse's 'SpatialData' class in R,
  as well as various methods to interact and visualize these data.
  The class contains 5 layers (images, labels, shapes, points, tables)
  that may contain an arbitrary number of elements; these are
  represented as objects of S4 classes 'ImageArray', 'LabelArray',
  'ShapeFrame', 'PointFrame' and 'SingleCellExperiment', respectively.
  The S4 'ZarrArray' class is implemented to represent images and labels
  with any 'A/array' representation (e.g., 'SparseArray', 'DelayedArray').
Depends: R (>= 4.3)
